      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milton%2C_Ulster_County%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "In 1844, Sumner Colman opened a wheel‑barrow factory at the same dock, expanding Milton’s early industrial base.",
